{"tid":976084,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"在岸人民幣升0.5%穿6.7  中間價創4個月高","createTime":"2019-01-10T06:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T07:42:52.000Z","uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"39005bff7c1c607668d731e13293805b3b981669","tid":976084,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T06:56:22.000Z","msg":"【在岸人民幣升0.5%穿6.7  中間價創4個月高】在岸人民幣升幅擴大至0.46%，報6.7849。離岸人民幣維持升0.3%，報6.7914。人民幣中間價調強366點，報6.8160，為去年8月30日以來新高。中美貿易談判結束，傳遞出或許有望達成協議從而結束貿易戰的謹慎樂觀基調。特朗普政府稱中國承諾採購更多的美國農產品、能源和製成品。中國商務部稱談判增進雙方了解，為解決彼此關切問題奠定了基礎。"},{"pid":"98be8e7661178893c3c78f23f76adfc3af8a792b","tid":976084,"uid":117947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T06:58:14.000Z","msg":"唉, 屌, 11月走晒"},{"pid":"53e3d42408c384a70e2c368a387ddcbd77924e88","tid":976084,"uid":13008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"98be8e7661178893c3c78f23f76adfc3af8a792b","tid":976084,"uid":117947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T06:58:14.000Z","msg":"唉, 屌, 11月走晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T06:58:50.000Z","msg":"milkmilk"},{"pid":"c3e417811606623e84cc77fd003aecaa9fe78129","tid":976084,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:42:52.000Z","msg":"大爆升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}